    "description": "Body text of the terminal auto-reconnect-failure surface (Epic #3013 phase 3). Explains the auto-reconnect gave up after bounded attempts and how to recover."
  },
  "obd2ReconnectRetry": "Erneut versuchen",
  "@obd2ReconnectRetry": {
    "description": "Label of the button that restarts the bounded auto-reconnect loop after it gave up (Epic #3013 phase 3, #3019). The user-actionable 'tap to retry' affordance the Epic requires."
  },
